Name:           flowbox-rpc
Version:        0.1
Cabal-Version:  >= 1.8
--License-file:   LICENSE
Author:         Flowbox <contact@flowbox.io>
Maintainer:     Flowbox <contact@flowbox.io>
Build-Type:     Simple


Library
    Hs-Source-Dirs: dist/gen,
                    src
    Other-Modules:  Paths_flowbox_rpc
    GHC-Options:    -Wall -O2 -threaded
    Extensions:     NoImplicitPrelude

    Exposed-modules: `findmodules('dist/gen', '.*\.hs', exclude='.*hs-boot.*')`,
                     `findmodules('src', '.*\.hs')`

    Build-Depends:  base,
                    bytestring,
                    containers,
                    either,
                    errors,
                    flowbox-utils-old,
                    mtl,
                    protocol-buffers,
                    protocol-buffers-descriptor,
                    transformers,
                    zeromq4-haskell >= 0.6
